data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome home to this spacious 2-story with 4 bedrooms + Bonus area upstairs with private full bath and TONS of upgrades. Built in 2021 but this immaculate home feels brand new! As you arrive, you will notice the extended paver driveway upgrade providing more space. The Simmitano floor plan by Lennar offers so much flexibility with split bedrooms and open floor plan. As you enter, the foyer leads to a hallway with two bedrooms that share a hall bath. Continue through to the great room with ceramic plank flooring throughout and space for a HUGE dining table to gather and open to the living room space as well! The spaciousness extends to the kitchen so you can watch TV or entertain while gathering around the huge island. The kitchen upgrades include 42 inch cabinets and Quartz countertops with Stainless steel appliances. Enjoy cooking or baking with plenty of counter space and a walk-in pantry. An additional bedroom with an attached bathroom is located to the other side of the entrance hall providing privacy for guests. The primary suite is at the back of the home, private from the other bedrooms, offering views into the backyard. The attached bathroom features dual sinks, garden tub, walk-in shower, and spacious walk-in closet! Upstairs a HUGE bonus room can be a media room, guest suite, home office for remote work, or school area with attached full bath. There is so much flexibility with this floor plan for whatever your household needs! All bathrooms feature Quartz countertops, stylish fixtures and a shower/tub combo. An indoor laundry room leads to the 2 car garage with ample space for cars or storage. All this and a perfect backyard to enjoy this fall! Step outside from the great room sliding glass doors to enjoy the covered lanai and extended paver patio with hot tub and fully fenced backyard! The owners upgraded this space to enjoy Florida living and it shows! NEW PVC fence, NEW gutters, NEW extended paver patio and more! Located in Tohoqua with a resort style swimming pool, clubhouse with a state of the art fitness center, tennis and pickle-ball courts and walking trails throughout the community. Why wait for new construction when you can have this practically brand new home already upgraded for your enjoyment now?! Schedule a showing today!
